{"tid":625269,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"利記名宿警告沙拿別離開利物浦 否則會變山齊士","createTime":"2018-04-11T10:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T11:14:42.000Z","uid":179467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9df6e6973649244c10bd248e462b06e618b072","tid":625269,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"今季沙拿加盟利物浦後入球不斷，目前以29球領跑英超射手榜，這讓他獲得了來自皇馬等豪門的關注。<br />\n　　利物浦名宿約翰-巴恩斯表示，「高普知道使用怎樣的戰術發揮出沙拿的最佳狀態，沙拿雖然是一名出色的球員，但他在這裡得到了最適合自己發揮出最大潛力的環境。如果沙拿為另一支球隊效力，我認為他的表現無法這麼優異。」<br />\n　　約翰-巴恩斯還用山齊士作為反面例子，「在我看來山齊士也是一名出色的球員，和沙拿同樣出色，但他在曼聯沒能展現自己的真實水平，因為他效力的球隊無法讓自己發揮出最佳狀態。並不是說山齊士的表現糟糕，而是摩連奴給球隊製定的戰術導致山齊士無法做到最好。」<br />\n　　（來自 肆客足球）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/8701749/1/20180410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F8701749%2F1%2F20180410&d=9Q56bAYsZhWDnGmmLrhNDuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=15c5f6a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/8701749/1/20180410</a><br />\n<br />\n今年猁諗下修仔降班後,有咩前鋒可以簽仲好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55aa1a0fd78949cf376f2a480f2080901311e80d","tid":625269,"uid":17669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"我利要邊個球員留就要留，否則通通係25仔"},{"pid":"5e129fd17fce907cfe1ba0b7b08aaf30b9103441","tid":625269,"uid":158791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"山齊士45萬磅週薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27848c179491862f11dcd442ef6ff82e4aafc651","tid":625269,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:02:48.000Z","msg":"有大會要點都走啦"},{"pid":"3c544eab9a32640c14e1bedc7190ce8a59d2b49e","tid":625269,"u